252
00:24:21,050 --> 00:24:25,565
Well, that's good. You said he has
resources the police don't have, right?

253
00:24:32,808 --> 00:24:34,798
Even so, um...

254
00:24:36,127 --> 00:24:38,321
I imagine you wish he were here.

255
00:24:47,965 --> 00:24:49,956
Hands out, please.

256
00:24:55,844 --> 00:24:59,632
- Turn around.
- Oh, enough. Maureen's an old friend.

257
00:24:59,724 --> 00:25:03,033
- It's all right. He's just doing his job.
- Thank you.

258
00:25:03,123 --> 00:25:05,636
Your ID, ma'am.

