261
00:25:14,281 --> 00:25:16,875
Come on, Senator. That's not fair.

262
00:25:16,961 --> 00:25:18,997
No, I'm just saying.

263
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:21,674
You, me, my family.

264
00:25:21,760 --> 00:25:23,751
We made a journey together,

265
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:26,718
