266
00:25:26,799 --> 00:25:30,678
We helped each other along,
because we cared about the same things.

267
00:25:30,759 --> 00:25:33,831
- I know that.
- Have I ever lied to you?

268
00:25:33,918 --> 00:25:36,591
- No.
- Embarrassed you?

269
00:25:36,678 --> 00:25:39,715
- No.
