278
00:26:12,872 --> 00:26:15,022
You owe me that much, at least.

279
00:26:17,032 --> 00:26:19,023
OK.

280
00:26:20,671 --> 00:26:22,549
Two sources.

281
00:26:23,871 --> 00:26:26,624
One, a man named George Ferragamo.

282
00:26:28,110 --> 00:26:30,908
He was your son's therapist for four years.

283
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:33,540
He came to me with the story.

284
00:26:35,229 --> 00:26:37,299
And the second source?

285
00:26:39,269 --> 00:26:44,422
The boy who raped your daughter, then
