00:33:28,128 --> 00:33:30,687
- 30...
- There they are.

368
00:33:31,687 --> 00:33:34,723
- OK, you can speed it up.
- All right. Speeding up.

369
00:33:36,246 --> 00:33:38,202
- Slow it down now.
- You got it.

370
00:33:38,285 --> 00:33:40,276
You got a mark on that car?

371
00:33:43,045 --> 00:33:45,764
- Coming to you now.
- All right.

372
00:33:46,524 --> 00:33:48,276
Where are you headed, Jack?

373
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,319
- All set?
- All set.

374
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,675
- How much time do you need?
- A few seconds.

375
00:34:23,279 --> 00:34:25,554
- Who are these guys?
- I told you. I don't know.

376
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:29,234
They tell me what to do.
I do it, they pay me. That's it.

377
00:34:29,318 --> 00:34:32,116
It's ringing.

378
00:34:32,197 --> 00:34:33,870
- Yeah?
- I'm not showing anything.

379
00:34:33,957 --> 00:34:35,072
Yeah?

380
00:34:35,158 --> 00:34:39,786
- It's a cellphone.
- We're screwed. I don't know the frequency.

381
00:34:40,197 --> 00:34:41,788
- I'll get back to you.
- Jack?

382
00:34:41,877 --> 00:34:44,595
- Yeah?
- It's Gaines. There's a change of plan.

383
00:34:44,676 --> 00:34:49,908
Nothing you can't handle. Taped to the back
of the phone is a set of keys with a remote.

384
00:34:52,315 --> 00:34:55,067
- Got 'em.
- It's for a parked car on Avenue 26.

385
00:34:55,154 --> 00:34:59,305
Nevada plates, 782NOF.
Find it with the remote.

386
00:34:59,394 --> 00:35:01,953
There's a body in the trunk. Get rid obit.

387
00:35:02,633 --> 00:35:04,624
- What does he mean, body?
- I don't know.

388
00:35:04,713 --> 00:35:07,307
- Whose body is in the trunk?
- I don't know!

389
00:35:23,790 --> 00:35:25,781
Walk in front of me.

390
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:28,623
Come on.

391
00:35:42,427 --> 00:35:46,943
Kneel up against that wall and interlock
your fingers behind your head. Now.

392
00:35:47,427 --> 00:35:49,656
Don't move.

393
00:35:54,185 --> 00:35:56,177
Oh, my God.

394
00:36:15,382 --> 00:36:17,896
- Hey, Jack.
- Hey, we had a deal.

395
00:36:17,982 --> 00:36:20,177
Shut up.

396
00:36:20,261 --> 00:36:22,980
- Put him in the car.
- Hey! Hey!

397
00:36:23,061 --> 00:36:24,699
Bauer!

398
00:36:24,781 --> 00:36:28,091
That's pretty quick work, George.
Trackin' me on a satellite?

399
00:36:28,181 --> 00:36:32,651
- I'm takin' you in, Jack.
- He had evidence on the Palmer hit.

400
00:36:32,739 --> 00:36:35,128
That's why I broke him out.

401
00:36:38,898 --> 00:36:41,618
- So who was this?
- I don't know yet.

402
00:36:45,538 --> 00:36:49,166
You're havin' quite a night here,
aren't you, Jack?

403
00:36:49,617 --> 00:36:52,256
Why don't you tell me
what the hell is going on here?

404
00:36:52,336 --> 00:36:56,649
