408
00:37:08,574 --> 00:37:11,088
I apologise if I was wrong.

409
00:37:11,174 --> 00:37:14,883
George, as crazy as this sounds,
you're gonna have to trust me.

410
00:37:14,973 --> 00:37:20,127
This is gonna look very bad for us
if something happens to Palmer tonight.

411
00:37:25,932 --> 00:37:28,890
- So what's next?
