420
00:38:17,404 --> 00:38:19,280
- Yes, Doctor.
- Clamp, please.

421
00:38:21,363 --> 00:38:23,399
Hello?

422
00:38:23,483 --> 00:38:26,395
- Hey. It's me.
- Jack, did you find out anything?

423
00:38:26,483 --> 00:38:29,155
- Maybe. I'm not sure yet.
