426
00:38:35,921 --> 00:38:38,640
Good. It's really important I talk to her.

427
00:38:38,721 --> 00:38:42,759
I know it sounds cold, sweetheart,
but she's our only link to Kimberly.

428
00:38:42,841 --> 00:38:46,071
Hang in there, honey.
I love you. I'm on my way, OK?

429
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,151
OK.

430
00:39:12,756 --> 00:39:14,747
Just be cool.

431
00:39:29,233 --> 00:39:32,509
We'd like our money now,
if that's like, you know, OK.

432
00:39:35,233 --> 00:39:40,181
Well, just so we're, like, you know, clear...
what happened to the other girl?

433
00:39:40,272 --> 00:39:43,263
Janet? It's like I told you. We had to kill her.

434
00:39:44,671 --> 00:39:46,946
My people say someone
fitting her description

435
00:39:47,031 --> 00:39:49,942
was taken to a hospital
near to where you were.

436
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:53,225
How do you explain that?

437
00:39:55,469 --> 00:39:57,585
Well, the thing is...

438
00:40:00,228 --> 00:40:02,743
Maybe, uh, she wasn't quite dead.

439
00:40:05,148 --> 00:40:08,777
Well, I'll tell you, Dan,
you're either dead or you're not dead.

440
00:40:08,867 --> 00:40:11,506
There's no such thing as sorta dead.

441
00:40:11,587 --> 00:40:13,338
Here. Let me show you.

442
00:40:13,587 --> 00:40:15,498
No!

443
00:40:22,225 --> 00:40:24,819
You've just been promoted.

